      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative specimen of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8. The powerplant features eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. Chassis dynamics are optimized with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock. This vehicle remains in concours-level condition; the rod bearings have been addressed preventatively, and the subframe shows zero signs of fatigue. The exterior retains its factory luster with consistent paint depth across all panels, complemented by forged Style 220M wheels. An investment-grade driving machine for the discerning purist.",
